Daruruwan mutane sun taru don bikin a bakin teku a birnin Palu a ranar Juma'a lokacin da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi mita shida (18 feet) suka yi karo da bakin teku da yamma, suka kwashe mutane da yawa zuwa ga mutuwarsu kuma suka lalata duk abin da ke cikin hanyarsu.
