"An gwada mu a wasanninmu har yanzu, kuma har yanzu ba a doke mu ba, don haka dole ne in yi farin ciki", in ji shi.
Robyn Christie na Melrose ya ce: "Godiya ga Ayr, sun yi amfani da damar su fiye da yadda muka yi".
Grant Anderson ya yi ƙoƙari a minti na 14, wanda Frazier Climo ya canza, ya sanya Ayr a gaba, amma, katin rawaya don Scotland cap Rory Hughes, wanda Warriors ya saki don wasan, ya ba Melrose damar yin lambobi kuma Jason Baggot ya kama wani ƙoƙari.
