LeBron zai fara buga wasan Lakers ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Jira ya kusan karewa ga magoya bayan da ke son ganin LeBron James ya fara wasa a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na ranar Lahadi a gaban Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma minti nawa zai yi wasa har yanzu ba a tantance ba.
"Zai fi daya kuma kasa da 48, " in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Dan jaridar Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasa a takaice.
Bayan atisayen da suka gabata, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasanni shida na Lakers na kakar wasa.
