Lokacin Taron Trump na Yammacin Virginia, Tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara gangamin gangamin yakin neman zabe a wannan daren a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin tarurrukan Trump guda biyar da aka tsara a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tare da kada kuri'ar tabbatar da zabensa na cike wa babban kotun da ke zaman kansa, Trump na da burin samar da goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar-lokaci mai zuwa tunda 'yan Republican na fuskantar hatsarin rasa iko da Majalisa lokacin da aka kada kuri'a a ranar Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump na yammacin Virginia zai gudana a yau kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon ta yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump na Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe 7 na yammacin yau, Asabar, Satumba 29, 2018.
Kuna iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shirye a YouTube.
Trump zai yi jawabi a wannan makon a zaman sauraron da aka yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mai tashin hankali kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i tare da sa ran kuri'ar tabbatar da majalisar dattijai da aka jinkirta har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan tarin tarukan shine taimakawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben Nuwamba su sami wasu karfin gwiwa.
Saboda haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan tarurruka biyar a mako mai zuwa suna da nufin "karfafawa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisa na da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandarsa wanda shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu yayin da muke shiga lokacin kamfen mai cike da aiki", in ji mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
An shirya taron na yau da dare a filin wasa na Wesbanco a Wheeling, zai iya kawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma janyo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh", a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci jihar ta West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa dole ne ya zo don ya ba shi ci gaba a cikin zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA ta nuna karfin gwiwa don yaki don ci gaba da fatan rayuwa a kan hanyar zuwa ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman guda uku, wasan hudu na ranar Asabar da yamma zai iya zama abin da wannan gasar ta Ryder Cup ke bukata.
Dandalin motsa jiki na motsi gaba ɗaya ƙirar ƙirar wasanni ce amma wacce 'yan wasa suka yi imani da gaske, kuma ba fiye da a gasa kamar wannan ba.
To, ina ne za su ce motsi yake yanzu?
"Suna da maki shida a gaba kuma yanzu ya kai hudu, don haka muna ɗaukar hakan a matsayin ɗan ƙaramin ƙarfi ina tsammanin", in ji Jordan Spieth yayin da yake tafiya don ranar.
Turai tana da fa'ida, ba shakka, maki huɗu a gaba tare da ƙarin goma sha biyu a cikin wasa.
Amurkawa, kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin suna da ɗan iska a cikin jirgi duk da haka kuma suna da abubuwa da yawa da za a ƙarfafa su, ba kalla ba ne siffar Spieth da Justin Thomas waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu yana alfahari da maki uku daga hudu.
Spieth ya kasance mai kisa daga tee zuwa green kuma yana jagorantar misali.
Wadannan kururuwan murna sun kara kara karfi yayin da zagayen ya ci gaba, yana nutsewa don daukar wasa na hudu duk-square lokacin da shi da Thomas suka kasance biyu bayan biyu.
Wasansa da ya lashe wasan a 15 ya samu karba karba irin wannan, irin wanda ya gaya muku cewa ya yi imanin cewa tawagar Amurka ba ta fita daga wannan ba.
"Ya kamata ka yi bincike sosai kuma ka damu da yadda za ka yi wasa", in ji Spieth.
Wannan shi ne abin da kowane ɗayan waɗannan 'yan wasan ya rage yanzu.
Rami 18 don yin alama.
'Yan wasa guda daya da suka samu maki fiye da Spieth da Thomas a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, labarin da ba a iya musantawa ba na gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Ma'aurata masu ban sha'awa amma masu ban sha'awa na Turai suna da hudu daga cikin hudu kuma ba za su iya yin kuskure ba.
"Moliwood" sune kawai ma'aurata da ba su harba ba a ranar Asabar da yamma, amma kuma sun guje wa baƙi a ranar Asabar da safe, ranar Juma'a da yamma da kuma baya tara a ranar Juma'a da safe.
Wannan gudu, da kuma yadda suke samun kuzari daga wannan taron da ke cike da hayaniya, ya tabbatar da cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su doke ranar Lahadi, kuma babu wani dan wasa da ya fi kowa shahara da zai tabbatar da nasarar Turai yayin da rana ta sauka a kan Le Golf National fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari.
Zai fi kyau duka a lokaci guda a kan ramuka daban-daban.
Amma, magana game da ɗaukaka ta Turai bai kai na farko ba.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi gajeren aiki na Sergio Garcia, jarumin kwallon kafa na safe, lokacin da aka haɗa shi da Alex Noren.
Wani mummunan abu da biyu biyu a kan gaban tara ya haƙa Spaniard da Swede cikin rami wanda ba su taɓa kusantar hawa daga ciki ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, ba wanda zai taimake ka ka fita daga cikin ramin.
Kwallan hudu da na hudu suna da ban sha'awa sosai don kallo daga kusa saboda hulɗar da ke tsakanin ma'aurata, shawarar da suke bayarwa, shawarar da ba su ba da kuma yadda dabarun za su iya canzawa a cikin wani lokaci.
Turai ta fi kyau a matsayin tawagar har zuwa yanzu kuma ta yi nasara sosai a ranar karshe amma wannan zaman hudu ya kuma nuna cewa Team USA tana da karfin gwiwa don gwagwarmaya da wasu, musamman na Stateside, suka yi shakku.
Turai ta yi nasara da ci 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder
Turai za ta yi amfani da kyakkyawar dama a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder bayan ta fito daga wasannin kwallaye hudu da hudu na ranar Asabar tare da jagoranci 10-6 akan Amurka.
Duka biyu masu wahayi Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci cajin tare da cin nasara biyu akan Tiger Woods mai gwagwarmaya don ɗaukar ƙididdigar su har zuwa yanzu a Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, da ke neman riƙe kofin da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta mamaye ƙungiyar Amurka da ke rashin nasara a wasannin hudu na safe, ta ci wasan 3-1.
Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a cikin hudu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba za su iya cinye rashi ba.
Jam'iyyar Jim Furyk na bukatar maki takwas daga wasannin guda 12 da suka yi a ranar Lahadi domin su rike kofin.
Fleetwood shine dan wasan Turai na farko da ya lashe maki hudu a jere yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da "Molliwood" bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki sune kawai biyu da suka lashe maki hudu daga wasannin farko hudu a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin kwallaye huɗu sai suka yi nasara sosai don doke Woods da ɗan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da ƙimar da ta fi ƙarfin 5 & 4.
Woods, wanda ya janye kansa ta hanyar wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu fitattun abubuwa amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin wasanninsa 29 a cikin kwallaye hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, ya huta don wasannin hudu na safe, ya koma abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a cikin hudu zuwa 2 & 1 nasara ga Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - na farko da na uku a duniya.
Turai ba ta da ita ta hanyar da ta dace ba duk da haka a ranar da take da iska mai iska a kudu maso yammacin Paris.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas sun kafa ma'auni ga Amurkawa da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara 2 & 1 akan Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a cikin kwallaye huɗu kuma suka dawo daga baya don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4 & 3 a cikin hudu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup ne wata tawagar ta dawo daga rashin maki hudu zuwa wasan guda, kodayake a matsayin masu rike da Furyk kawai suna bukatar su ci nasara don riƙe kofin.
Bayan sun kasance na biyu mafi kyau na kwana biyu, duk da haka, wani hari na ranar Lahadi kamar dai ba za su iya ba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce 'ba zai yiwu' ta kwance makamai ba tare da amincewa ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin da ake ci gaba da yi na kara kara kara rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma babu yadda kasar za ta daina amfani da makaman nukiliya a cikin irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron kungiyar na shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakai masu kyau" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman, lalata wurin gwajin nukiliya, da kuma alƙawarin kada a yada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga wani martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da wani amincewa da Amurka ba za a sami amincewa a cikin tsaronmu na kasa kuma a irin wannan yanayi babu yadda za mu iya cire makamai da kanmu".
Duk da yake Ri ya sake maimaita korafe-korafen da aka saba da su na Koriya ta Arewa game da juriyar Washington ga tsarin "matakai" na kawar da makaman nukiliya wanda a karkashinsa za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada yayin da ta dauki matakai na hankali, sanarwar sa ta bayyana mai mahimmanci a cikin cewa ba ta ƙi kawar da makaman nukiliya ta gefe ɗaya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka fitar a taron koli na farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don "rashin makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbacin tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na neman kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta daina makaman nukiliyarta da farko.
Washington ta kuma yi adawa da kira don sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa mai tsanani kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan "kawar da makaman nukiliya da farko" kuma tana kara matsin lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma manufarsu ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma tana adawa da "bayyanar da ƙarshen yaƙi", "in ji Ri.
"Tunanin cewa takunkumi na iya kawo mu a kan gwiwoyinmu mafarki ne na mutanen da ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, takunkumin da ake ci gaba da yi yana ƙara sa mu rasa amincewa".
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba wanda shugaban Amurka ya nuna a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Maimakon haka ministan ya nuna tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya kara da cewa: "Idan bangaren wannan batun na kawar da makaman nukiliya ya kasance Koriya ta Kudu ba Amurka ba, kawar da makaman nukiliya na yankin Koriya ba zai kai ga irin wannan matsi ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bamban da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya fadawa Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa kai hari ga Amurka da makaman nukiliya na Koriya ta Arewa ba makawa bayan "Mista Shugaban Sharri" Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin roka" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "halaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin zuciyarsa wajen ɗaukar matakan kawar da makamai, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne takunkumi su kasance har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokacin da zai yi wannan, yana cewa "Idan ya ɗauki shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar - ba kome ba ne".
Sin da Rasha sun yi jayayya cewa ya kamata kwamitin sulhu na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ba Pyongyang lada saboda matakan da ta dauka.
Amma, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amirka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da tilasta wa Majalisar Tsaro ta hana yin amfani da makaman nukiliya har sai mun samu cikakken, ƙayyadadden, kawar da makaman nukiliya".
Majalisar Tsaro ta amince da tsaurara takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 a kokarin da take yi na hana Pyongyang samun kudade don shirin nukiliya da makamai masu linzami.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma ya ce bayan haka zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma tafiyarsa ta karshe ba ta tafi da kyau ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana cewa an samu ci gaba, kawai don Koriya ta Arewa a cikin sa'o'i don la'antar shi don yin "bukatun kamar 'yan bindiga".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a wani taro da Moon a wannan watan don rushe wani wurin makami mai linzami da kuma hadadden makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki "matakan da suka dace".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa "matakan da suka dace" da yake nema su ne tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma motsi zuwa daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna koyon yadda za su samu isashen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara ya sa dukan ɗalibansa su sami ƙarin barci a ƙoƙarin su yaƙi al'adar ƙwararrun mutane na yin karatu ta 'dukan dare' da ke cike da maganin kafeyin.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗalibai a jami'a mafi girma a duniya sau da yawa ba su san ainihin yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Makarantar Likita ta Harvard kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da na Mata, shi ne ya tsara wannan darasi, wanda ya yi imanin shi ne na farko a irin wannan a Amurka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi ya fara wannan hanya bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
'A ƙarshen taron wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce: 'Me ya sa ake gaya mini wannan yanzu, a shekarata ta ƙarshe?'
Ta ce babu wanda ya taɓa gaya mata game da muhimmancin barci - abin da ya ba ni mamaki,' in ji shi a The Telegraph.
Darasin, wanda aka fara gabatar da shi a wannan shekara, ya bayyana wa ɗalibai muhimman abubuwan da suka shafi yadda halayen bacci mai kyau ke taimakawa aikin ilimi da wasan motsa jiki, da kuma inganta lafiyarsu gaba ɗaya.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a makarantar likitanci ta Harvard kuma babban daraktan ayyukan kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi bayan gano cewa dalibai suna fama da rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Darasi na awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi jerin ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A wani sashe akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai ke danna kofuna na kofi, labule, masu horo da littattafai don a gaya musu game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda aikin motsa jiki ke shafar rashin bacci, da kuma muhimmancin tsarin bacci.
A wani sashe, an gaya wa mahalarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya kara hadarin bugun zuciya, bugun jini, bakin ciki da ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar, tare da gumaka masu ma'amala, sannan yana ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da ayyukan su na yau da kullun.
'Mun san ba zai canja halayen ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun yi imanin suna da hakkin su sani - kamar yadda kuke da hakkin ku san illar shan sigari ga lafiyarku", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adar alfahari da 'ja da dare' har yanzu tana nan, in ji shi, ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da kuma karuwar matsin lamba a kan dalibai na nufin rashin bacci ya kasance matsala mai girma.
Ya ce tabbatar da samun isasshen bacci, mai inganci, ya kamata ya zama 'makamin sirri' na ɗalibi don yaƙi da damuwa, gajiya da damuwa - har ma don kauce wa samun nauyi, kamar yadda rashin bacci ke sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, yana sa su ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, wani ɗan California mai shekara 19 da yake nazarin ilimin sunadarai da ilimin halittu, ya taimaki Farfesa Czeisler ya tsara wannan darasin, ya halarci ɗaya cikin darussansa a shekarar da ta shige a shekara ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce karatun ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya sa shi ya tura don karatun a duk faɗin harabar.
Mataki na gaba, yana fata, shi ne a nemi dukkan daliban digiri na biyu su kammala irin wannan shirin karatu kafin su shiga cikin cibiyar gasa.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da saita ƙararrawa don lokacin da za su kwanta, da kuma lokacin da za su farka, kuma su san mummunar tasirin 'haske mai shuɗi' da allunan lantarki da hasken LED ke fitarwa, wanda zai iya jefa saurin circadian dinka cikin rikici, wanda ke haifar da matsalolin barci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Menga ta ci wa mutanen Gerrard kwallo
Rangers sun sake fuskantar wani mummunan yanayi yayin da Dolly Menga ta kai hari a hannun Steven Gerrard wanda ya rasa nasara a Livingston da ci 1-0.
Kungiyar Ibrox na neman samun nasarar farko a kan hanya tun bayan nasarar 4-1 da ta yi a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta yi wa Gerrard kashi na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin koci don barin tawagarsa maki takwas a baya da shugabannin Ladbrokes na Premier Hearts.
Menga ya buga minti bakwai kafin rabin lokaci kuma Rangers line-up short a kan wahayi ba ya kama da daidaitawa.
Yayin da Rangers yanzu suka sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa na uku kuma kawai a baya Hibernian a bambancin burin.
Kuma za a iya samun karin matsala ga masu tsaron bayan da aka yi wa Calum Spence da ke kula da layin layi magani saboda ciwon kai bayan da aka jefa wani abu daga gefen gefe.
Gerrard ya yi sauye-sauye takwas a cikin kungiyar wanda ya wuce Ayr zuwa wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya tafi da Livi 11 daya wanda ya dauki maki daga Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda kayan aikinsa suka shawo kan abokan hamayyarsu a kowane lokaci.
Rangers na iya mamaye mallaka amma Livingston ya yi fiye da yadda suke da kwallon.
Ya kamata su ci kwallo ne kawai a minti biyu lokacin da aka dakatar da Menga a karon farko ya tura Scott Pittman a kan Allan McGregor amma dan wasan tsakiya ya janye babbar damarsa.
Babban Keaghan Jacobs kyauta-kick sa'an nan kuma ya sami kyaftin Craig Halkett amma abokin aikinsa Alan Lithgow ya iya kawai ya yi wuka a baya.
Rangers sun kama iko amma akwai fatan da yawa fiye da imani game da wasan su a cikin kashi na uku na ƙarshe.
Alfredo Morelos tabbas ya ji ya kamata a yi masa hukunci a alamar kwata-kwata yayin da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo amma alkalin Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da roƙon dan wasan na Colombia.
Rangers sun gudanar da harbi biyu ne kawai a farkon rabin wasan amma tsohon mai tsaron raga na Ibrox Liam Kelly ya sha wahala kadan daga ci gaban Lassana Coulibaly da kuma bugun Ovie Ejaria.
Duk da yake wasan farko na Livi na minti na 34 na iya zama a kan wasan, babu wanda zai iya musun sun cancanci hakan saboda allurar da suka yi.
Har yanzu Rangers sun kasa magance zurfin Jacobs.
Scott Arfield bai yi martani ba yayin da Declan Gallagher ya jefa kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya riƙe sanyi don ya zaɓi Menga don kammala sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu yayin da ya canza Coulibaly don Ryan Kent kuma sauyawa kusan ya ba da tasiri nan take yayin da mai tsaron ya shiga Morelos amma Kelly mai ban sha'awa ya gudu daga layinsa don toshewa.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da jan hankalin baƙi don yin wasa daidai irin wasan da suke jin daɗi, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna share dogon kwallon bayan dogon kwallon.
Holt na iya karawa da gaba a matakai na karshe amma McGregor ya tsaya da kyau don ya hana Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya tashi daga kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton ya sake yin wani korafi na karshe don hukunci yayin da ya shiga cikin Jacobs amma kuma Thomson ya kalli gefe.
Almanac: Wanda ya kirkiro na'urar lissafin Geiger
Kuma yanzu shafi daga "Sunday Morning" Almanac: Satumba 30, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce, da kuma kirga ... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna aikin rediyo, abin da ya kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger Counter.
Babban ginshiƙin kimiyya tun daga lokacin, Geiger Counter ya zama babban ginshiƙin al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda a cikin fim ɗin 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya ƙunshi waɗannan masana kimiyya masu ban mamaki Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Gidan Geiger ne, da ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adanai masu aiki da hasken rana, kamar su uranium.
Sa'ad da ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin da atoms suke yi daga aikin rediyo da ke cikin ma'adanai".
Evans: "Ka ce, hakika yana fashewa yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ya cika shekara 63.
Amma abin da ya ƙirƙira da sunansa ya ci gaba da rayuwa.
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa za ta iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ta "ga" ƙwayoyin cuta
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa za ta iya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki ta "ga" ƙwayoyin cuta da ke kashe su
Rigakafin ya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki gane ƙwayoyin cuta a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani
Hanyar tana ɗauke da cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga cikin marasa lafiya, canja su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje
Sai su 'ga' wani furotin da ya zama ruwan dare ga yawancin cututtukan daji, sa'an nan su sake saka shi
Wani allurar rigakafin gwaji na nuna kyakkyawan sakamako a cikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da nau'ikan cututtukan daji.
Wata mata da aka yi mata allurar rigakafin, wadda take koya wa tsarin garkuwar jiki gane ƙwayoyin cuta, ta ga ciwon daji na cikin mahaifa ya ɓace na fiye da watanni 18.
Wannan hanyar tana ɗauke da cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga jikin mai ciwo, a canja su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don su "ga" wani furotin da ake kira HER2, wanda ya zama ruwan dare a yawancin cututtukan daji, sa'an nan a sake saka ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon Ciwon daji ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa muna da maganin da zai yi mana kyau".
HER2 "yana sa ciwon daji iri-iri ya yi girma", har da ciwon nono, na kwayar halitta, na huhu da kuma na ciki, in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
Irin wannan tsarin, wato, cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga jikin marasa lafiya da kuma "koyar da" su yadda za su kai hari ga ƙwayoyin ciwon daji, ya yi nasara wajen magance wani irin cutar sankarar bargo.
