Bayan ya yi waka ta uku a daren, mai suna Ghost Town inda yake sanye da hat na Make America Great, ya yi ta yin tir da 'yan Democrat kuma ya sake jaddada goyon bayansa ga Trump.
"A lokuta da dama ina magana da fararen fata kuma suna cewa: "Ta yaya za ku so Trump, shi dan wariyar launin fata ne?"
