Tauraruwar Game of Thrones Kit Harington ta yi nasara a kan mazaunin da ke da guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da yake yi a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na HBO mai ban tsoro na Game of Thrones .
Amma dan wasan, mai shekaru 31, ya yi watsi da ra'ayin jarumin macho, yana mai cewa irin wadannan rawar a kan allon suna nufin cewa matasa maza sukan ji kamar dole ne su kasance masu karfi don a girmama su.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin 'wani abu ya ɓace' kuma ya yi tambaya kan yadda za a magance matsalar ƙarancin maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri 'yar wasansa ta Game of Thrones Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana jin 'da gaske' game da magance batun.
'Ina jin kaina, sosai, a yanzu - ina muka yi kuskure game da namiji? ' in ji shi.
'Me muka koya wa maza a lokacin da suke girma, dangane da matsalar da muke gani yanzu?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya kasancewa wani ɓangare na haɓakar ƙarancin maza saboda yawan halayen maza.
Ya ci gaba: 'Menene a cikinmu kuma menene aka koya mana?
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin, da kuma a kan titi, da ke sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su kasance da wannan bangare na kasancewa namiji?
Ina tsammanin wannan shine ainihin ɗaya daga cikin manyan tambayoyin zamaninmu - ta yaya zamu canza hakan?
Domin a bayyane yake cewa akwai wani abu da bai dace ba game da samari.'
A cikin hirar ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones ba ko kuma ci gaba lokacin da jerin ya ƙare a lokacin bazara, yana cewa ya 'yi tare da fagen fama da dawakai'.
Daga watan Nuwamba Kit zai yi rawar gani a wani farfado da Sam Shepard na True West wanda shine labarin wani mai shirya fim da dan uwansa, wanda shine mai fashi.
A kwanan nan, dan wasan ya bayyana cewa yana ganin saduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya fito daga Game of Thrones.
'Na sadu da matata a wannan wasan kwaikwayon, don haka a wannan hanyar ta ba ni iyalina na gaba, da rayuwata daga yanzu,' in ji shi.
Rose ta buga Ygritte, ƙaunar ƙaunar halin Kit Jon Snow, a cikin jerin wasan kwaikwayo na Emmy.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yunin 2018 a kan filayen gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta bayar da rahoton karuwar kashi 14% na sabbin masu kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan 'yan kasarta da ke rayuwa da cutar HIV da kuma cutar AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu a ƙasar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
Kimanin sabbin mutane 40,000 ne aka samu a kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Mafi yawan sabbin cututtukan sun kamu ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A al'ada, cutar HIV ta bazu da sauri a wasu ɓangarorin China sakamakon ƙarin jini da ke ɗauke da cutar.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a kowace shekara, adadin waɗanda suke da HIV da Aids a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i matsala ce mai tsanani a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a China a 1997, amma ana cewa nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT ya zama ruwan dare.
Domin ƙa'idodin ƙasar da suke da tsauri, bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90% na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza a ƙarshe za su auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka da ke yaduwa daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin China ta yi alkawarin samun magani na HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa ma'aikatanta sun leaked bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijai na GOP, ta fashe da' karya mai haɗari 'da kuma' ra'ayoyin makirci '
'Yar majalisar wakilai ta Amurka Maxine Waters a ranar Asabar ta yi tir da zargin cewa wani memba na ma'aikatanta ya sanya bayanan sirri na 'yan majalisar dattijai uku na Republican a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
The Los Angeles Democrat ya tabbatar da cewa masu bincike da shafukan yanar gizo na "tsakiya na dama" suna yin amfani da waɗannan da'awar.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya, da kuma ƙarin ƙazantacciyar ƙarya", in ji Waters a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
Rahotanni sun ce bayanan sun hada da adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na U.S. Sen. Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka biyu daga Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani ba a san shi ba ya wallafa a Capitol Hill yayin sauraron majalisar dattijai kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Fashewar ta zo ne bayan da 'yan majalisar dattijai uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ruwaito cewa adireshin IP wanda ke gano asalin sakonnin yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma ya saki bayanin wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, Hill ya ruwaito.
"Wannan zargi mara tushe ba gaskiya ba ne kuma karya ce", Waters ya ci gaba.
"Mambobin ma'aikatana - wanda aka yi wa asirinsa, da bayanansa, da kuma amincinsa barazana sakamakon waɗannan zarge-zargen na yaudara da na ƙarya - ba su da alhakin ɓarkewar wannan bayanin.
Wannan zargi marar tushe ƙarya ce kuma ba gaskiya ba ce".
Sanarwar Waters da sauri ta jawo suka a yanar gizo, gami da tsohon sakataren manema labarai na Fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
Fleischer ya rubuta: "Wannan ƙin yarda yana da fushi.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da halin zama mamba a majalisar.
Idan aka zargi wani da wani abu da bai yi ba, kada su yi fushi.
Kada su yi tawaye.
Kada su yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa mai zargin yake zarginsa.
Dole ne su kasance da kwanciyar hankali".
