Johnny Turanci Ya Sake Sake Sake sake dubawa - Rowan Atkinson mai tsattsauran ra'ayi
A yau al'ada ce a nemi ma'anar Brexit a kowane sabon fim da ke da ma'anar Biritaniya kuma hakan na iya dacewa da wannan farfadowar fim din Johnny English na wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo - wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake farfadowa a 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn.
