Na ji daɗin yadda Johnny English yake zuwa jirgi mai saukar ungulu da ya saka rigar yaƙi na zamanin da kuma yadda ƙyallen rotor ɗin yake rataye a kan kwalkwali.
Kyautar Atkinson don wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri yana kan nuni, amma wasan kwaikwayo yana jin daɗi sosai kuma ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman ma a matsayin alamun fim "mai tsanani" kamar 007 da Mission Impossible kansu yanzu suna ba da kyauta a matsayin kayan aiki.
Abin dariya yana jin kamar an yi shi ne ga yara maimakon manya, kuma a gare ni baƙon abin da Johnny English ya yi ba shi da hankali kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim din fim a cikin mutum na Bean.
