Don haka Batman da Robin na samun abubuwa da ba daidai ba a cikin Sirrin Sirrin Mai Girma sun dawo cikin aiki, suna fuskantar kyakkyawar matar Olga Kurylenko Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, firaministan ya fada cikin hatsarin da ya shafi mai karfin fasaha wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Birtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
