Jam'iyyar Labour ba za ta kasance farkon wanda ya goyi bayan irin wannan ra'ayin ba, tare da Jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin yin aiki na kwana hudu a cikin mako a lokacin yakin neman zaben 2017.
