Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Global Citizen zai ga dubun dubatan mutane suna ta yawo a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayo kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawo karshen matsanancin talauci nan da shekarar 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka bayyana a shekarar 2012, wani fadada ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ce ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Domin samun tikitin kyauta don taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikitin VIP), masu halartar kide kide da wake dole ne su kammala jerin ayyuka, ko "ayyuka" kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci.
