Amurka na iya amfani da Sojan Ruwa don " toshewa " don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Cikin Gida
Washington na iya "idan ya zama dole" ta yi amfani da rundunar sojan ruwanta don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwannin, ciki har da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke ya bayyana, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta nakalto.
