Lt Col Reverend Bernard Vann ya lashe kyautar a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba na 1918 a cikin harin a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Koyaya, wani dan bindiga ya kashe shi bayan kwana huɗu kuma bai taɓa sanin cewa ya sami babbar girmamawar sojan Burtaniya ba.
'Ya'yansa biyu sun kaddamar da wani abin tunawa a wani gangami a Rushden, Northamptonshire, ranar Asabar.
