A cewar Jaridar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 Laftanar Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta tsallaka Canal de Saint-Quentin "ta cikin hazo mai kauri kuma a ƙarƙashin wuta mai ƙarfi daga filin da bindigogi".
Daga baya ya ruga zuwa layin wuta kuma tare da "babban ƙarfin hali" ya jagoranci layin gaba kafin ya yi amfani da bindiga a hannunsa kuma ya kashe uku daga cikin rukunin.
An kashe Lieutenant Colonel Vann ta hanyar dan wasan Jamus a ranar 4 ga Oktoba 1918 - kawai fiye da wata daya kafin yakin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa "wani abu ne da na sani ba zan iya rayuwa ba amma wani abu ne mai tawali'u".
Shi da dan uwansa Dr James Vann sun kuma sanya wreath bayan bikin, wanda kungiyar matasa ta Brentwood ta jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce "yana jin daɗin taka rawa a cikin farar hula" kuma ya kara da cewa "ƙarfin gwarzo na gaske yana nunawa ta hanyar goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su bayar".
MMA magoya sun zauna duk dare don kallon Bellator 206, sun sami Peppa Pig a maimakon
