Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, inda ake sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Tare da katsewar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga gundumar Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke ƙarshen kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da kafa shi sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala yanki ne mai tsawon kilomita 300 (180 miles) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Regency, yanki ne na yanki a ƙarƙashin lardi, yana da yawan jama'a 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kamun kifi da noma sune manyan abubuwan da ke ci gaba da tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi an maida hankali ne a Morowali, a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
Tsunami ya afka wa Palu da Donggala sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, in ji Hukumar Kula da Yanayin Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan yankin da ke da ikon girgiza ƙasa a cikin Tekun Fasifik kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14 inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gaɓar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ruwa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afka kudu da Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya yi karo da gaɓar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta afka kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afkawa daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, a gabar Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 wanda ya lalata kauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai zurfi ta afkawa gundumar Pidie Jaya a Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba yayin da mutane suka tuna da lalacewar girgizar kasa da tsunami mai hallaka a shekarar 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami ba a wannan lokacin, amma sama da mutane 100 sun mutu sa'ad da gine-gine suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin yawon bude ido na Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin wani yanayi.
