Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa na musamman ga wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas -- hukunci mai wuya da ba a yi ba a jihar don aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a gefen Yammacin Hanya a Lower Manhattan, yana yanka masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke a hanyarsa a ranar Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov "da gangan" ya kashe wadanda aka kashe takwas kuma "da gangan" ya yi mummunan rauni, bisa ga sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa, da aka gabatar a Kudancin Yankin New York.
Dukkanin waɗannan zarge-zargen suna iya kaiwa ga hukuncin kisa, bisa ga takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, babban alƙalin tarayya ya yi wa Saipov hukunci da tuhumar da ta ƙunshi zarge-zarge guda takwas na kisan kai a cikin taimakon cin hanci, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a cikin shari'o'in aikata laifuka, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma shiri", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana hanyar da Saipov ya aiwatar da shi a matsayin "mai banƙyama, mai zalunci da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da kuma Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lahani, da kuma hasara", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan tun lokacin da aka yi shari'ar hukuncin kisa a Kotun Kudancin New York.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi guda biyu amma daga karshe aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
Lokaci na ƙarshe da aka zartar da hukuncin kisa a cikin shari'ar tarayya ta New York shi ne a 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an same su da laifin yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin Yakin Cacar Shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenbergs duka biyu ta wurin kujera mai lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, ɗan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadama a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya bayyana wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗi game da abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya samu kwarin gwiwa wajen kai harin ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi a nuna tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya amsa laifinsa na laifin da aka tuhume shi da shi.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "a bayyane yake sun yi takaici" da shawarar mai gabatar da kara.
"Muna ganin shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar laifin da za a yi masa da rai a gidan yari ba tare da yiwuwar sake shi ba zai kara tsawaita raunin wadannan abubuwan da suka faru ga duk wanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta riga ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Dan majalisar Tory ya ce ya kamata a bai wa NIGEL FARAGE aikin gudanar da tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin 'karfafa rundunar jama'a' a yau yayin zanga-zanga a taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban Ukip ya ce dole ne 'yan siyasa su ji zafi' daga masu shakkar Yuro - kamar yadda daya daga cikin 'yan majalisar Theresa May ya ba da shawarar ya kamata ya kasance mai kula da tattaunawa da EU.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Bone ya shaidawa masu zanga-zangar a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya 'za ta fice' a yanzu idan Mr Farage ne Sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen sasantawa tsakanin 'yan majalisa da ke da rabuwa sosai ya bayyana ne ta hanyar 'yan Tories masu goyon bayan ci gaba da zama a kasar da suka shiga wata zanga-zanga daban da suka yi a birnin na Brexit.
Firayim Minista na gwagwarmaya don kiyaye shirin sulhunta na Chequers a kan hanya a cikin hare-haren daga masu goyon bayan Brexit, Remainers da EU.
Al'ummomin da ke da alaka da ita sun dage cewa za ta ci gaba da kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da rashin amincewar da aka samu - kuma ta tilasta wa masu shakkar Turai da kuma 'yan Labour su zabi tsakanin kunshin da take bayarwa da kuma "ruwan rikici".
Mista Bone ya gaya wa taron barin barin barin barin a Solihull cewa yana son 'chuck Chequers'.
Ya ce ya kamata a sanya Farage a matsayin takwaransa kuma a ba shi alhakin tattaunawa da Brussels.
'Da a ce shi ne ke da iko, da mun riga mun fita,' in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: 'Zan tsaya kan Brexit amma muna bukatar mu kori Chequers.'
Da yake bayyana adawarsa ga EU, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi ba a yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama masu biyayya.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.'
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da ra'ayoyin cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun bayan zaben 2016: "Tunanin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son ci gaba da kasancewa ba gaskiya bane".
Tory Brexiteer Andrea Jenkyns ma yana wajen gangamin, yana gaya wa manema labarai: 'Ina kawai cewa: Firayim Minista, saurari mutane.
'Chequers ba shi da kyau a cikin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su yi zabe a kansa ba, ba shi da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma masu fafutukarmu waɗanda suka yi ta faman titi kuma suka sa aka zabe mu a farkon wuri.
Don Allah ka daina yin magana da su kuma ka fara saurara.'
A cikin wani sako da ta aika wa Mrs May, ta kara da cewa: 'Shugabannin ministoci suna rike da aikinsu idan sun cika alkawuransu.'
Mista Farage ya ce dole ne a sa 'yan siyasa su ji zafi idan suna shirin cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
'Yanzu batun dogara ne tsakaninmu - mutane - da kuma rukunin siyasa,' in ji shi.
'Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu' ba za mu bari ku fita da yin hakan ba '".
A cikin wani sako ga taron masu sha'awar ya kara da cewa: 'Ina son ku sa 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke gab da cin amanar Brexit, su ji zafi.
'Muna tattara sojojin jama'ar wannan kasa da ta ba mu nasara a Brexit kuma ba za mu taɓa hutawa ba har sai mun zama mai zaman kanta, mai mulkin kansa, mai alfahari da Burtaniya.'
A halin yanzu, Remainers sun yi tafiya ta Birmingham kafin gudanar da gangamin sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar gari.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi ta yin taho da banners na Tories Against Brexit bayan kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen makon nan.
Abokin aikin Labour Lord Adonis ya yi wa 'yan Conservatives ba'a saboda matsalolin tsaro da suka sha wahala tare da aikace-aikacen jam'iyyar yayin da aka bude taron.
"Waɗannan su ne mutanen da ke gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT a wurin da kuma duk fasahar don Kanada da ƙari, don iyakar da ba ta da matsala, don cinikin kyauta ba tare da iyaka a Ireland ba", in ji shi.
'Wannan abin dariya ne.
Babu irin wannan abu kamar Brexit mai kyau,' ya kara da cewa.
