Gasar Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a raga a madadin Giants a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi kafara da rashin nasarar da suka yi a ranar Juma'a a gasar Elite League da Belfast Giants ta hanyar lashe wasan dawowa da ci 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun samu nasara da kwallaye biyu a farkon wasan ta hanyar buga kwallo daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun kawo matakin gida kafin Dwyer ya dawo da jagorancin Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita wa Dundee kafin kwallo biyu na Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya tabbatar da nasarar su.
Wannan shi ne karo na uku da kungiyar Adam Keefe ta yi rashin nasara a gasar Elite League a kakar bana, inda suka zo daga baya don doke Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a da daddare.
Wannan ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin suka hadu a kakar wasa, inda Giants suka lashe wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya fara wasa a minti na huɗu a 3:35 daga taimakon Kendall McFaull, tare da David Rutherford yana ba da taimako yayin da Beauvillier ya ninka jagoranci bayan minti huɗu.
A lokacin da aka fara aiki, Sullivan ya dawo da 'yan wasan gida a wasan a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya zama mai samar da kwangilar Cownie a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun jagoranci a farkon hutu lokacin da ya buga burinsa na biyu na dare a ƙarshen farkon.
Ƙungiyar gida ta sake haɗuwa kuma Bouchard ya sake sanya su a kan daidaituwa tare da burin wasan motsa jiki a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun hada kai don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee jagoranci a karon farko a wasan a ƙarshen lokacin na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasara tare da wasan na biyar na tawagarsa a ƙarshen lokacin.
Giants, wadanda yanzu suka yi rashin nasara hudu daga cikin wasanninsu biyar na karshe, suna gida ne a Milton Keynes a wasansu na gaba a ranar Juma'a.
Mai Kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya mutu domin tabbatar da daruruwan mutane a cikin jirgin zasu iya tserewa girgizar kasa
Ana yabon wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia a matsayin jarumi bayan ya mutu yana tabbatar da cewa jirgin sama mai dauke da daruruwan mutane ya tashi lafiya daga kasa.
Fiye da mutane 800 ne suka mutu kuma da yawa sun bace bayan wata babbar girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, ta haifar da tsunami.
Girgizar kasa mai karfi na ci gaba da addabar yankin kuma mutane da yawa sun makale a cikin tarkace a birnin Palu.
Amma duk da abokan aikinsa da suka gudu domin tsira da rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung mai shekaru 21 ya ki barin matsayinsa a hasumiyar kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Filin jirgin saman Palu.
Ya zauna don tabbatar da cewa Jirgin Batik Air na 6321, wanda ke kan titin jirgin a lokacin, ya sami damar tashi lafiya.
Sai ya yi tsalle daga hasumiyar kula da zirga-zirga lokacin da ya yi tunanin za ta rushe.
Ya mutu daga baya a asibiti.
Kakakin kamfanin jirgin sama na Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce shawarar ta iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, in ji ABC News na Australia.
Mun shirya jirgi mai saukar ungulu daga Balikpapan a Kalimantan don mu kai shi wani babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin takaici mun rasa shi da safiyar yau kafin jirgi mai saukar ungulu ya isa Palu.
Ya daɗa cewa: "Zuciyarmu ta yi rawa sa'ad da muka ji wannan.
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na fargabar cewa adadin wadanda suka mutu na iya kaiwa dubbai tare da hukumar rage bala'in bala'i ta kasar ta ce samun damar zuwa garuruwan Donggala, Sigi da Boutong yana da iyaka.
"An yi imanin cewa adadin mutanen da suka mutu na ci gaba da ƙaruwa tun da gawarwaki da dama suna ƙarƙashin tarkacen jirgin yayin da ba a iya samun mutane da yawa ba", in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Rawanin ruwa da ya kai mita shida ya lalata Palu wanda zai gudanar da jana'izar jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na soja da na kasuwanci suna kawo taimako da kayayyaki.
Risa Kusuma, wata uwa 'yar shekara 35, ta gaya wa Sky News: "Kowanne minti motar agaji tana kawo gawawwaki.
Ruwa mai tsabta yana da wuya.
Ana yin fashi a dukan wuraren da ake sayar da kayayyaki".
Jan Gelfand, shugaban kungiyar Red Cross ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN cewa: "Kungiyar Red Cross ta Indonesia tana gaggawar taimakawa wadanda suka tsira amma ba mu san abin da za su samu a can ba.
Wannan bala'i ne, amma zai iya ƙara muni".
Shugaban Indonesia Joko Widodo ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin kasar: "Ina rokon ku duka ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala duk ayyukan da suka shafi kwashe mutane.
Shin kuna shirye?" in ji CNN.
A farkon wannan shekarar an yi wa Indonesia girgizar kasa a Lombok inda mutane sama da 550 suka mutu.
Hadarin jirgin sama na Micronesia: Air Niugini yanzu ta ce mutum daya ya bace bayan hatsarin jirgin saman lagoon
Kamfanin jirgin sama da ke gudanar da jirgin da ya yi hatsari a wani tafkin tekun Pacific a Micronesia yanzu ya ce mutum daya ya bace, bayan da ya ce a baya duk fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin sun kwashe jirgin da ke nutsewa lafiya.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce a cikin sanarwar cewa a ranar Asabar da yamma, ba zai iya lissafin wani matafiyi namiji ba.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin gari, asibitoci da masu bincike don kokarin gano mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin bai amsa nan da nan ba game da ƙarin bayani game da fasinja, kamar shekarunsa ko asalinsa.
Jiragen ruwa na gida sun taimaka wajen ceto sauran fasinjoji da ma'aikatan bayan jirgin ya fadi ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin saman Tsibirin Chuuk.
Jami'ai sun ce a ranar Juma'a cewa an kai mutane bakwai asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce fasinjoji shida sun kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar, kuma dukkansu suna cikin kwanciyar hankali.
Abin da ya haifar da hadarin da kuma ainihin jerin abubuwan da suka faru har yanzu ba a bayyana ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da Sojojin Ruwa na Amurka duk sun ce jirgin ya sauka a cikin tafkin kusa da titin jirgin.
Wasu shaidu sun yi zaton jirgin ya yi tsalle a kan titin.
Fasinja dan Amurka Bill Jaynes ya ce jirgin ya sauka a ƙasa sosai.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau ƙwarai", in ji Jaynes.
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu sun yi nasarar shiga cikin ruwa mai zurfin kagu zuwa hanyoyin fita na gaggawa a jirgin da ke nitsewa.
Ya ce ma'aikatan jirgin suna cikin fargaba suna ihu, kuma ya sha rauni a kai.
Rundunar sojin ruwan Amurka ta ce masu aikin jirgin ruwa da ke aiki a kusa da inganta wani tashar jirgin ruwa sun kuma taimaka wajen ceto ta hanyar amfani da jirgin ruwa mai kumfa don fitar da mutane zuwa gabar teku kafin jirgin ya nutse a kusan mita 30 (100 feet) na ruwa.
