Pelosi ta yi wannan tsokaci ne a wata hira da ta yi ranar Asabar a bikin Texas Tribune a Austin, Texas.
"Ba zan iya taimakawa ba sai dai in yi tunanin cewa idan mace ta taɓa yin hakan, za su ce 'histerical,'" Pelosi ta ce game da yadda ta yi wa Kavanaugh shaida a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai a ranar Alhamis.
