Ministan harkokin wajen Syria ya ce 'shirye' ne don 'yan gudun hijira su koma
Syria ta ce a shirye take don dawowar 'yan gudun hijira da son rai kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina kasar da ta lalace sakamakon yakin da ya shafe sama da shekaru bakwai.
Da yake jawabi a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin kasar na inganta.
"Yau halin da ake ciki a kan kasa ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro godiya ga ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da al'ada.
Dukkan yanayi yanzu suna nan don dawowar 'yan gudun hijira da son rai zuwa ƙasar da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da matakan tattalin arziki na gefe guda wanda ke niyya ga rayuwarsu ta yau da kullun da rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka gudu daga kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yaƙin a shekara ta 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da har yanzu suke zaune a kasar suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi maraba da taimako wajen sake gina kasar da aka lalata.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba za ta yarda da taimakon da aka tanada ko taimako daga kasashen da suka tallafa wa 'yan tawayen ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Team Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 inda ta doke Team USA da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National dake wajen birnin Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a jere a ƙasar Turai kuma ba ta ci kofin Ryder a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambin ne yayin da tawagar kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da suka buƙaci don doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa kwallon sa a cikin ruwa a rami na par-3 na 16, yana barin wasan sa ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiyanci Molinari ya haskaka a duk zagayensa, ya zama dan wasa daya daga cikin hudu da ya taba zuwa 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya yi taho da 5&4 daga dan wasan da ya fi kasa a cikin kungiyar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya fadi da 2 da 1 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe.
Tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup takwas, dan kasar Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi nasara a gasar tare da maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
