Sabuntawar Red Tide: Hanyoyin sun ragu a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Sabon rahoton da Hukumar Kifi da Dabbobin daji ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna raguwar yawan Red Tide a sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, ana ba da rahoton yanayin fure mai fure a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Counties Collier - wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
A bloom Red Tide yana fadada kimanin kilomita 130 na gabar teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudancin Lee.
Ana iya samun patches kimanin mil 10 a gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma a wurare kaɗan idan aka kwatanta da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da Red Tide a Pasco County.
An bayar da rahoton matsakaitan taro a cikin ko a gefen tekun Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan zuwa manyan taro a gefen tekun Hillsborough County, bayanan zuwa manyan taro a cikin Manatee County, bayanan zuwa manyan taro a cikin ko a gefen tekun Sarasota County, bayanan zuwa matsakaitan taro a cikin Charlotte County, bayanan zuwa manyan taro a cikin ko a gefen tekun Lee County, da ƙananan taro a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da bayar da rahoton tashin hankali na numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma Colier.
Ba a bayar da rahoton cutar numfashi ba a Arewa maso Yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
